			<article class="media testimonial">
				<div class="media-content text-left">
					<div class="content">
						<h2>Senior Cadet</h2>
						<h3>AS 400</h3>
						<p>I joined ROTC because I did JROTC in high school and loved it and wanted to continue with a similar program. I love becoming super close to my fellow cadets and how everyone supports each other through everything. <strong>Det 165 does an amazing job at improving everyone and never leaving anyone behind</strong>.</p>
						<p>ROTC has forced me to realize that you need to continuously push yourself past your comfort zone to improve and succeed. ROTC has also helped me to <strong>become more outgoing and a better leader in all aspects of my life</strong>.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
