				<div class="media-content text-right">
					<div class="content">
						<h2>Senior Cadet</h2>
						<h3>AS 400</h3>
						<p>Military service has become a lifestyle for me. I grew up in Germany and South Korea on a military base. Being involved in AFROTC feels like continuing the family business. <strong>I want to give back everything that's been given to me</strong>.</p>
						<p><strong>This program builds leaders</strong>. As a Air Force reservist at Maxwell AFB, I wanted to put myself in an environment where I could develop as a leader, and impact the mission on a different level. </p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>


			<article class="media testimonial">
