						<p>I joined ROTC <strong>to be a part of something greater than myself</strong>, and to be able to work with our country's cutting edge technologies.
						<p>I love how tight knit our detachment is&mdash;everyone gets to know each other really well, especially within your class. I think ROTC has made me a more motivated person, and I have made some <strong>lifelong friendships</strong> already.</p>
					</div>
